title: 2010 Sex Express Coffee (MEX)
description:
A police detective by the name of Escobar is handed over a very bizarre case: a man has been found cut into pieces inside his refrigerator. As the police investigations continue Escobar is implicated in twisted story of revenge that will take him to explore the urban legend known of "Sex Express;" inside a chat room a man lurks for sexual encounters with unknown youngster to give them the HIV virus.

Police detective Escobar attempts to capture an HIV+ internet predator who lures unsuspecting young men into sexual encounters while investigating the case of a man who was chopped into pieces and stuffed in his own refrigerator.
